
@startuml dfd-level0
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #222
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor white
skinparam arrowColor #222

title DFD Level 0 — Context Diagram

rectangle "Client / Frontend" as CLIENT
rectangle "Administrator" as ADMIN
circle "AC Supply Chain\nAnalytics System" as SYS
database "PostgreSQL 17" as DB
rectangle "Resend Email" as EMAIL
rectangle "ML Models\nRF · ARIMA · IsoForest" as ML
rectangle "AI Agent" as AGENT

CLIENT --> SYS : credentials, orders,\nML requests, agent chat
SYS --> CLIENT : KPIs, forecasts,\ndelay risk, AI alerts

ADMIN --> SYS : user mgmt,\nETL trigger
SYS --> ADMIN : reports,\nrecommendations

SYS <--> DB : reads & writes\n(SQLAlchemy)
SYS --> EMAIL : password reset emails
SYS <--> ML : inference requests\n& predictions
SYS <--> AGENT : queries / responses
@enduml